Package com.jmex.physics

Class Summary
DynamicPhysicsObject DynamicPhysicsObject is a PhysicsObject with dynamical properties, such as mass, velocity, applied forces etc.
PhysicsObject A PhysicsObject is a wrapper around a jME Spatial (the graphical representation) and its physical ODE corresponding.
